UPDATE designer_curator_picks SET description = CASE id
  WHEN '278b92e0-0db3-4796-a926-67f108738c04'::uuid THEN 'The Dais lounge chair by Alexander Lamont is a masterwork of sculptural seating that balances tactile warmth with rigorous artisanal precision and a distinct presence. This sophisticated piece features sumptuous bouclé upholstery contrasted against the meticulous texture of hand-applied shagreen leather and intricate straw marquetry accents. Representing a bridge between Eastern craft traditions and mid-century European elegance, the chair embodies the designer’s commitment to rare, decorative materials and innovative luxury craftsmanship. Every silhouette reflects a pursuit of refined, multi-textured materiality, resulting in a functional objet d’art that anchors a contemporary interior with its sophisticated and sculptural aesthetic.'
  WHEN '200b1808-cbfd-45ab-bc1a-26f0dadf787b'::uuid THEN 'The Galea Lantern by Alexander Lamont is a luminous masterwork that captures the intersection of natural mineral beauty and rigorous artisanal craftsmanship. This ceiling light features a meticulously hammered bronze base that serves as a sculptural foundation for the organic interplay of radiant rock crystal and frosted glass shades. Reflecting the atelier’s dedication to rare materials and early twentieth-century decorative influences, the fixture transforms functional illumination into a profound artistic statement. The piece highlights a shared devotion to meticulous workmanship, resulting in collectible lighting that resonates with a timeless sculptural presence and sophisticated elegance for refined contemporary interiors.'
  WHEN 'b18599da-7e4b-40b0-9cf0-bdc633ee3096'::uuid THEN 'The Koi Carps decorative sculptures by Alexander Lamont capture the fluid elegance of aquatic movement through masterful bronze casting. Each piece showcases a rich bronze patina that highlights the meticulous craftsmanship synonymous with the brand’s dedication to rare materials and sculptural presence. This wall art serves as a poetic bridge between Eastern tradition and contemporary refinement, reflecting the studio''s philosophy that art connects us to memory. Perfect for sophisticated interiors, these bronze accents bring a distinct, timeless luminosity to any curated collection of luxury objets d’art through their meticulously worked surfaces and evocative, flowing forms.'
  WHEN '03eab06e-b1c1-4039-93a7-102ec95ddd98'::uuid THEN 'The Moiré Table Lamp by Alexander Lamont is a sculptural masterpiece that reinterprets the fluid visual depth of watered silk through meticulous Amethyst Ikat straw marquetry. This elegant lighting piece features fine dyed inlays that create shifting tonal gradients across its rhythmic surface, capturing a distinct contemporary presence. A custom Cadenza handwoven fabric shade by Anne Corbière crowns the design, harmonizing rare natural textures through exceptional craftsmanship. Marrying traditional artisan techniques with a sophisticated silhouette, Alexander Lamont delivers a luminous decorative object that transforms atmospheric illumination into an intimate expression of luxury, material innovation, and timeless global influence.'
  WHEN '455d6a81-964c-4f76-8fc3-9f60bf5b39fd'::uuid THEN 'The Ondas Sconce by Alexander Lamont is a sculptural masterwork that unites twentieth-century decorative influences with the precision of contemporary artisan craftsmanship. Expertly realized in hand-cast bronze, this elegant wall light features a clear glass diffuser that emits a warm, directional glow through its meticulously textured metal silhouette. As a cornerstone of collectible lighting, the piece exemplifies Lamont’s signature intersection of organic forms and rare materials, bringing a refined, tactile presence to luxury interiors. This sophisticated fixture celebrates the power of traditional casting techniques, transforming architectural surfaces with its luminous, East-meets-West aesthetic and a distinct, artful soul.'
  WHEN 'dde884b1-569b-4afd-bacb-dece5b61a516'::uuid THEN 'The Otto Table Lamp by Alexander Lamont is a sculptural masterpiece of collectible lighting that embodies the designer’s commitment to rare materials and meticulous craftsmanship. Hand-finished in natural distress shagreen, this evocative piece reflects a bridge between Eastern and Western aesthetic influences, drawing inspiration from the luminous decorative arts of the early twentieth century. Each lamp functions as an intimate expression of artistry, transforming high-end interiors into gallery-like sanctuaries through its storied textures and refined silhouette. This Alexander Lamont creation honors the power of fine objects, blending historical luxury with a contemporary design language for the discerning collector.'
  WHEN '1d619c2a-3553-436c-86c4-3666d52584d3'::uuid THEN 'The Plume Table Lamp by Alexander Lamont is a sculptural masterpiece that bridges early twentieth-century European elegance with Japanese aesthetic refinement. This exquisite lighting piece showcases the atelier’s signature straw marquetry, hand-applied in a sophisticated Dusk Ombré palette that transitions with poetic fluidity. Each surface radiates a soft, luminous glow, highlighting the meticulous craftsmanship and rare materiality synonymous with the British designer’s Bangkok studio. By marrying traditional artisan techniques with a contemporary monotone sensibility, the lamp serves as a profound expression of luxury, bringing a textured, artisanal presence to the most discerning modern interiors and curated living spaces.'
END
WHERE id IN ('278b92e0-0db3-4796-a926-67f108738c04'::uuid,'200b1808-cbfd-45ab-bc1a-26f0dadf787b'::uuid,'b18599da-7e4b-40b0-9cf0-bdc633ee3096'::uuid,'03eab06e-b1c1-4039-93a7-102ec95ddd98'::uuid,'455d6a81-964c-4f76-8fc3-9f60bf5b39fd'::uuid,'dde884b1-569b-4afd-bacb-dece5b61a516'::uuid,'1d619c2a-3553-436c-86c4-3666d52584d3'::uuid);